%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-EhbmJp2hi9HLiXQfO6maGA">Thái Diễm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-V%C4%A9/H%E1%BB%93i-h%C6%B0u-l%C6%B0u-gi%E1%BA%A3n-thi/poem-W2fudiqzy7dfV32I0iyn4A">Hồi hưu lưu giản thi - 回休留柬詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-V%C4%A9/author-aP_eFMQeGWFWrGEB_-u0wA">Nguyễn Đức Vĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/M%C3%B4-ng%C6%B0-nhi/poem-kotueSADUs76XWra40hfkQ">Mô ngư nhi - 摸魚兒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A0nh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-_3Q8NyAr4CRqKgdIYAsADA">Thành thượng - 城上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/Thu-v%C3%A3n-Linh-V%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%B1-chung-l%C3%A2u-nh%C3%A0n-v%E1%BB%8Dng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-pSNagIAVj-rAvyZdlBRZVQ">Thu vãn Linh Vân tự chung lâu nhàn vọng kỳ 1 - 秋晚靈雲寺鍾樓閒望其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/author-IUtlhs85uNhJ4NvGicsgMg">Bùi Huy Bích</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
